OL,3,CIsle of Man Constabulary targets
OL,4,Ctransferees from UK to join island
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FThe Chief Constable of the Isle of Man
OL,8,FConstabulary hopes to "attract
OL,9,Ftransferees from UK forces" as part of
OL,10,Fthe police recruitment drive.
OL,12,FRuss Foster says while he expects the
OL,13,Fconstabulary to be operating at 'full
OL,14,Fstrength' this year, additional
OL,15,Fofficers are needed ahead of the TT
OL,16,Fraces.
