OL,3,CIsle of Man Constabulary targets
OL,4,Ctransferees from UK to join island
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FMembers of the constabulary have taken
OL,8,F'workshops' to areas in the North
OL,9,FWest, the Midlands, and areas of
OL,10,FGreater London, hoping to convince
OL,11,Fpeople to move to the Isle of Man.
OL,13,FMr Foster said: "We're trying to
OL,14,Fattract transferees from UK forces who
OL,15,Fwant a different quality of life over
OL,16,Fhere on the Isle of Man.
OL,18,F"We are the third safest country in
OL,19,Fthe world, we're certainly the safest
OL,20,Fplace in the British Isles, and that
OL,21,Fremains our focus."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
