OL,7,FFollowing negotiations with the
OL,8,FDepartment for Home Affairs, part of
OL,9,Fthe constabulary's recruitment drive
OL,10,Fhas seen an increase in salary for
OL,11,Fthose joining the Manx police.
OL,13,FMr Foster said: "Our student officers
OL,14,Fstart on just over #35,000 per annum,
OL,15,Fwhich after three years rises to
OL,16,F#50,000.
OL,18,F"That's put us in a position where
OL,19,Fwe're more competitive with the public
OL,20,Fsector, with other emergency services
OL,21,Fand other law enforcement agencies.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
