OL,7,F"And as a consequence, we've seen a
OL,8,Fmuch diverse range of student officers
OL,9,Fand we've certainly attracted people
OL,10,Ffrom other professions."
OL,12,FThe Chief Constable reflected on the
OL,13,Fchallenge of recruitment, as leader of
OL,14,Fthe force for almost three years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
