OL,3,CIsle of Man Constabulary targets
OL,4,Ctransferees from UK to join island
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FHe said: "I was sworn in in April
OL,8,F2023, we had a vacancy rate of 24
OL,9,Fpolice officers, and throughout the
OL,10,Fyear, that was set to increase further
OL,11,Fdue to retirements and people
OL,12,Fresigning - so it's certainly been a
OL,13,Fchallenge for us.
OL,15,F"However, three years on and we've
OL,16,Fmanaged to recruit 38 police officers,
OL,17,Fand today is a bit of a milestone
OL,18,Fwhere we've welcomed eight new
OL,19,Fconstables who've started their
OL,20,Ftraining here at Port Erin training
OL,21,Fcentre."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
