OL,4,Ctransferees from UK to join island
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FWhile the constabulary is still below
OL,8,Fthe desired number of officers, they
OL,9,Fsay this should be increased in time
OL,10,Ffor the TT races in May.
OL,12,FMr Foster said: "I think at a last
OL,13,Fcount we're down to approximately nine
OL,14,Fofficers below our funded strength.
OL,15,FWe're about to start another
OL,16,Frecruitment drive, and I'm hoping
OL,17,Fbefore the TT period starts, we will
OL,18,Fbe fully up to strength."
